short.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G: Provide Code templates for various algorithms

long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G:
Neet is a browser extension designed to streamline the coding process for developers, particularly during programming contests or coding sessions. It provides a collection of high-quality algorithm and data structure templates in various programming languages.
With Neet, developers can access and copy code snippets without having to switch tabs, making it incredibly convenient and time-saving.
Want to contribute? Checkout github repo!
If you find this helpful, please rate it!
Happy Coding!
